HOW TO READ THIS LEGEND
------------------------
Each layer entry shows:
  - Layer name and data source
  - Symbol description (line weight, color description, style)
  - Scale visibility (when the layer appears/disappears as you zoom)
  - Label behavior (what text appears and at what zoom)

Scale reference:
  Statewide overview  =  1:500,000 and smaller (zoomed out)
  Regional            =  1:100,000 – 1:200,000
  Area planning       =  1:35,000 – 1:75,000
  Field navigation    =  1:10,000 – 1:35,000
  Close / site detail =  1:1,000  – 1:10,000

